/design

# Vendored ACP agent assets. Both the codex-acp native binary
# (~170 MB per platform) and the claude-agent-acp JS wrapper tree
# (~33 MB after stripping tests) are fetched via
# scripts/fetch-acp-binaries.sh from pinned npm registry versions.
# Keeping them out of git keeps `git diff` legible and version bumps
# tracked through the script's pinned constants.
apps/desktop/src-tauri/binaries/codex-acp-*
apps/desktop/src-tauri/resources/acp/node_modules/
apps/desktop/src-tauri/resources/acp/.claude-acp.version
